
DEPENDENCIES
============

Guillotine has the following rubygem dependencies:

  treetop
  facets

To work with Guillotine, the following rubygems are also required:

  rake
  hoe
  newgem
  rspec
  rcov
  diff-lcs
  flog (soon)
  activerecord

Here it is, all in one command:

  sudo gem install rake hoe newgem rspec rcov diff-lcs flog treetop facets activerecord